Sentencas: In the present work we describe a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) that comprises a Ni/GDC cermet anode, doped with a potentially commercially viable concentration of gold nano-particles.
Titulo: Au-doped Ni/GDC as a new anode for SOFCs operating under rich CH4 internal steam reforming

Sentencas: Specifically, gold was applied prior to anode sintering via the deposition-precipitation method.
Titulo: Au-doped Ni/GDC as a new anode for SOFCs operating under rich CH4 internal steam reforming

Sentencas: This procedure resulted in a SOFC that allowed carbon tolerant operation at T = 850 degrees C under fuel rich internal steam reforming of methane, with a stable power density of 0.41 W cm(-2) at 810 mV for over 200 h. (C) 2010 Professor T. Nejat Veziroglu.
